# Supported templates

To start a project follow this:

```bash
cd projects/guides
# or
cd projects/examples

# Templates compatible with the project objective

dotnet new web -n <project-name> -o <project-dir>
dotnet new grpc -n <project-name> -o <project-dir>
dotnet new webapi -n <project-name> -o <project-dir>
dotnet new mvc -n <project-name> -o <project-dir>
dotnet new blazor -n <project-name> -o <project-dir>
dotnet new blazorwasm -n <project-name> -o <project-dir>
```
